---
title: Creamy Truffle Penne with Beef plus Onion & Peas
description: Thanks to a few delicious tricks of the trade, you’ll have this luxurious and comforting creamy truffle pasta on the table in a quick 25 minutes! The first shortcut is our cream sauce base which you’ll combine with sautéed onion to start this savory, velvety sauce. Add garlicky browned ground beef, sweet peas, and tender penne to the mix, and for the final trick, sprinkle on a generous dose of truffle zest, which elevates this humble pasta to the next level with its distinctive bold, earthy flavor.
